Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.27,0:00:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's the deal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.90,0:00:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just capturing your future on film.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.57,0:00:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? It's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.70,0:00:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your future has been photographed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.78,0:00:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It depicts you lying on the ground after losing this Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I'll believe that bogus photo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't change a future that's been photographed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,0:00:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was decided the moment I flashed my shutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.64,0:00:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All photos I shoot depict the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it is sure to... become a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.91,0:01:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that darn Shark... really Dueling for revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.50,0:01:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will exact revenge on you here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.67,0:01:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yuma, don't get involved with me anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.42,0:01:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.42,0:01:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just Shark... Even that IV guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.72,0:01:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Such painful and twisted expressions!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.60,0:01:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It shines only during my service!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.81,0:01:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take my fanservice!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dueling isn't a tool for revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.27,0:01:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duels aren't meant to hurt people!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.94,0:01:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All Duelists are friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.53,0:01:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.83,0:01:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look Yuma! It's a blimp!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be a special occasion to celebrate the opening of the Carnival!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.12,0:01:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe riding it will lift your spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's look at Heartland City from up in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.30,0:01:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unacceptable! There's no excuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.30,0:01:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No excuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.68,0:02:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're supposed to be friends! We're supposed to enjoy ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.64,0:02:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, obviously we're all friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we should cheer each other up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.73,0:02:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.35,0:02:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, gawd!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you so worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, just do whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you go after her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotori seems to be really worrying about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Just keep out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.53,0:02:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I get closer, I stretch my hand out
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}towards that shining light leading towards tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.42,0:02:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I dream of a world that expands from my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.26,0:03:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I haven't a clue of where things like dreams and hopes are at.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.77,0:03:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I run looking for it, I still can't seem to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.23,0:03:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if I have fallen into a gap of truth and lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.73,0:03:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even so, our grand tale has yet to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.95,0:03:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's move on towards tomorrow, \Neven if our road begins to fall apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will jump forward, before all my\N strength completely drains.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.88,0:03:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The closer I get, the further it becomes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that truth that I must seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's to find hope that we desire from a future unseen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With a heart stronger than anyone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.60,0:03:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll learn to keep running up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.89,0:03:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the strength to win any battle, \Ndespite just how weak I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.61,0:03:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My purpose is to find,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.61,0:03:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with these invaluable friends of mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.61,0:04:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The future of the world expanding\N from my feet with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuuta Hayami?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that freelancer photographer you\N were talking about, editor-in-chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(474,507)}"Number 35: The Shocking Scoop!\N Kotori's Dangerous Future!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You told the guy, "It needs to have a bigger impact" and claimed he would give us a trashy reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But lately, he's been able to capture major events on camera before any other journalists even got a chance to report on them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That amateur photographer somehow managed to capture one scoop after another on film before anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He shocked many experts around the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have absolutely no idea, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I realize you have other work, but I want you to make contact with this Shuuta Hayami and collect data on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:05:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anyway, I want you to convince him to enter a contract with our company's monopoly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our sources tell us he is a participant in the Duel Carnival.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His current location is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God, why me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's that photo supposed to be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This depicts your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you see in these pictures will happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can change the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:06:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can then reveal that future in the form of a photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is why I will never lose in a Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you also didn't have a Number?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These photographs were taken before this actually happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean he can really control the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.74,0:06:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then all the scoops he captured on film up until now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:07:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What were you doing? I'm in a hurry here, so answer immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You've heard of Shuuta Hayami, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iyami?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's Hayami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should know him if he's participating in the Carnival, shouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do you take me for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know a guy like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't allow him to create any more incidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidents? Whatcha mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuuta Hayami seems to have the power to make any future he sees in his mind become a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't fully believe it 100% myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I saw him take a picture of the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they let a guy like that into the Duel Carnival?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know why. And since I don't know why, I'm investigating.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But with that power of his, he can't lose a Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.81,0:07:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anyway, if you find Shuuta Hayami, I want you to contact me immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, what gives?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't lose because he can see the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:08:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if there is any truth to it, there's a chance this person might be possessed by a Number.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By a Number?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is cause for investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, go find him. This man named Shuuta Hayami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God, every single one of 'em ordering me around... Who do you people think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Kotori?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where'd she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She left a while ago after you said some terrible things to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did that to Kotori? Like heck would I ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotori! Kotori?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Observation #17: "When human beings hurt one another with their words, they have no memory of it afterward."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I understand how you feel, Kotori.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Yuma really wants to be by himself, I'll just go up in the sky by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say cheese, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look this way! Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upperclassman!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upperclassman Hayami!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been about a year or so since I took that picture of you, Mizuki-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, and it looks so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it was a bit embarrassing when it was chosen to be shown in the arts festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it made me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I consider that photo to be one of my greatest works.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:10:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a very pleasant middle school memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.07,0:10:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The smiles on those kids' faces...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still take such nice pictures that really bring out the charm of those in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah. Let me take a new shot using the blimp as the background.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! Of course you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I can't believe I have to find this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.00,0:10:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even now this Iyami, er, I mean Hayami's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:11:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to spot him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like there's a Duel over there. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.39,0:11:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.78,0:11:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-There's no way something in a picture can come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's flat out impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack the enemy Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure-Kill First Grade Shot!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Just as I said it would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were fated to be buried in three turns.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I captured all of it on the pictures I shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they are sure to become reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:11:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These pictures...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.27,0:12:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He predicted the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can control the future just like my big sis said!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you all right?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get him to a hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he really was using a Number.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.21,0:12:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they Dueling like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Hayami?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! Why can't you just enjoy Dueling?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duelists are supposed to be friends, so why do you need to go that far?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that obvious? It's so I can obtain Numbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, that man earlier wasn't a Numbers holder.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my search will continue!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:13:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I can obtain all the Numbers in the entire world!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing so will produce even {\i1}greater{\i0} photos!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll continue shocking everyone all over the world by capturing unbelievable pictures of big scoops!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's trying to gather the Numbers all on his own!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you know about the existence of Numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could... Could you possibly...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I have some!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! So you have Numbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do! But I'll never let a guy like you-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I told you to inform me the second you found him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.46,0:13:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember me, Shuuta Hayami?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess I can't blame you for not remembering an amateur reporter like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I bet you remember the editor-in-chief of the Net News who rejected all of your pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:13:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you bet I remember him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:14:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He belittled me severely and told me, "News photos need to have a bigger impact"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now the editor-in-chief wants to enter a contract with you, bit I won't accept that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I could ever acknowledge a guy who puts the lives of others in danger
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just to be the first to capture pictures of a big scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I put their lives in danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm shocked! I'm simply trying to capture "nice pictures"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.59,0:14:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're using this weird power you got that lets you change the future to do so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lets him change the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did this before, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said something like, "The future will move as I command it to."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes, I can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using the power of the Numbers, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose you won't believe it until you see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like the power of the Number this man is being controlled by has the power to control the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Control?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you these pictures, so please hurry and get out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no doubt that the editor-in-chief will be more than pleased with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see anyone joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to Duel this guy over here, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, don't do it. You can't Duel with such a dangerous guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you call yourself a reporter, surely you don't have the time to laze about here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I'll give you a little present that will give you another really big scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one may make you nauseous, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.98,0:15:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it can't he helped, since you cornered me like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotori!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotori-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Are you two by any chance acquaintances of this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, you had best hurry along.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An incident will occur soon, you see, where that blimp has a wee bit of engine trouble in the skies of Heartland City.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That photograph there holds within it the coming of one of the largest scoops to ever strike this area to be caught on film.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if it should happen... No, all of my photos are bound to become reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you can bet Heartland City will be lead into a big panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.44,0:16:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now hurry along and show the editor-in-chief that picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once that picture of the incident hits the web, the entire world will feel its impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do something so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Stupid", indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotori! Answer me, Kotori!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kotori!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why are you contacting me now for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere you'll never find me, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.00,0:16:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't tell me... On the blimp?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you riding on that blimp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.47,0:16:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you bet I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, I'm having a blast up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.47,0:16:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels good to look at that city like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that! I mean, is there anything out of the ordinary?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? Out of the ordinary?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotori!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.78,0:16:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:16:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The engine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What about the engine?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotori!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.54,0:17:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to stop this at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No can do, because this just became reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one who made it reality, right?! Return it to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy do you ever shock me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a reporter, you should be jumping for joy right about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.10,0:17:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are reporters? They seek out scoops, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitting me won't change this reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And while we waste our time like this, the blimp draws ever closer to its impending peril.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do something about the blimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare take your eyes off this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally that nagging pest's gone away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how about we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the one being controlled by a Number loses the Duel and has the Number taken away,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they should return to normal, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:17:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:18:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning if I beat this guy, the future depicted in that photo will disappear and Kotori will be safe, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.43,0:18:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spot on. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Shuuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Disk, set!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Gazer, set!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}AR Vision - Link established.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Target, locked on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the heck are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm capturing your future on film!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Your future is depicted right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It shows you after you lose this Duel and have all your Numbers taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future shown in these pictures cannot be changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My victory and your miserable defeat was decided the moment I flashed my shutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My future won't be decided by someone like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking the first turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a Monster in face-down Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll set a card face-down and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Scoop Shooter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.99,0:19:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Monster Yuma set face-down in Defense Mode was Gogogo Golem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It has 1500 Defense Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On the other side, Scoop Shooter has 1400 Attack Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If he attacks like this, the opponent will receive damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:20:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Equipment Magic, Telephoto Lens, from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I equip Telephoto Lens to Scoop Shooter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Monster equipped with this card gains 400 Attack Power for each card in my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.19,0:20:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have four cards in my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it gains 1600 Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's got 3000 Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it's okay. Gogogo Golem can't be destroyed by the opponent's Monster in battle once per turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then activate the Magic Card, Negative -> Positive Swap, from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card forces a face-down Defense Monster to switch into face-up Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.60,0:20:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And their Attack Power is switched with their Defense Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using Negative -> Positive Swap reduced my hand by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.69,0:21:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Scoop Shooter's Attack Power goes down 400 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A slight drawback...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this will be more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.03,0:21:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Scoop Shooter!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Gogogo Golem!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We have urgent news.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.39,0:21:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It seems the blimp flying over Heartland City's skies is currently experiencing engine trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.86,0:21:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay. I promise it'll be okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.94,0:21:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Kotori!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.61,0:21:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise I'll help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.45,0:21:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.16,0:21:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been decided! The picture you saw before was just the outcome,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.45,0:21:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this entire Duel is depicted in these pictures here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:22:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the fifth turn, you will Summon No. 39, Aspiring Emperor - Hope,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.50,0:22:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and on the sixth turn, you will be defeated by {\i1}my{\i0} Number.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.05,0:22:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future has been captured within these photographs!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.43,0:22:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they will not fail to become reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.09,0:22:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someone gave me some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.63,0:22:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I was able to paint a rainbow with ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.31,0:22:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to become someone perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.89,0:22:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it's very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.27,0:22:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even with me suffering,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.86,0:22:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't seem to grasp victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.70,0:22:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.16,0:23:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I must be having some kind of weird dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.08,0:23:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But If I must fulfill this,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.62,0:23:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then I don't mind being laughed at for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.58,0:23:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since it's because your limits are decided on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.80,0:23:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll show it, overcoming it to tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.80,0:23:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah, I'm aiming for the big blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.22,0:23:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For all of its glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.95,0:23:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Freesia of Desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All of those countless flower petals
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.36,0:23:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They came at the expense of
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.03,0:23:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}me being able to reach those heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.14,0:23:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah, even though I lost my way today,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.37,0:23:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I still yearn for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.04,0:23:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That Freesia of Desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.82,0:23:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future he created using the power of the Numbers...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.45,0:23:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lose this Duel and Kotori will perish on board the blimp...!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.20,0:24:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there no way for us to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.75,0:24:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this keeps up...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.46,0:24:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who said you decide your own future.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.75,0:24:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can muster up the courage to bring it to 'em, I can change the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.30,0:24:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Yu-Gi-Oh! ZeXal!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.26,0:24:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,""Power To Open A Path To The Future! Hope Ray, The Lord Of Hope"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.81,0:24:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna bring it to 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.35,0:24:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's review the Heart Pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.56,0:24:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pieces are all broken up and not all of them fit each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.48,0:24:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The players decide how many pieces they bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.15,0:24:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta hurry and collect five Heart Pieces so I can complete my heart!
